      "url": "/wol/d/r101/lp-cv/202026169?#h=1:0-32:0",
      "imageUrl": "/wol/d/r101/lp-cv/202026169/thumbnail",
      "caption": "mwb26 Mayo p. 15",
      "content": "<header>\r\n<h1 class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-color--textSubdued\" id=\"p1\" data-pid=\"1\"><span id=\"page15\" class=\"pageNum\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-no=\"15\" data-before-text=\"15\"></span>HUNYO 29–HULYO 5</h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-margin-top--2 du-margin-top-desktopOnly--4\" id=\"p2\" data-pid=\"2\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\"><strong>JEREMIAS 11-12</strong></a></h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"bodyTxt\">\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p3\" data-pid=\"3\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/0/0\"><strong>Awit 106</strong></a> <strong>ug Pag-ampo | Introduksiyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(1 min.)</span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt7\" class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 dc-icon--gem dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--teal-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p4\" data-pid=\"4\"><strong>BAHANDI GIKAN SA PULONG SA DIYOS</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt9\" class=\"dc-bleedToArticleEdge dc-paddingToContentEdge du-bgColor--bgSecondary du-margin-top--8 du-padding-top--8 du-padding-bottom--1\">\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p5\" data-pid=\"5\"><strong>1. Kon Unsaon nga ‘Makapakiglumba Ka sa mga Kabayo’</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt11\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt12\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p6\" data-pid=\"6\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"p7\" data-pid=\"7\">Ingong mga Saksi ni Jehova, makadahom gyod tag mga pagsupak, sama kang Jeremias (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 11:21</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/1/0\"><em>w04</em> 11/1 16 ¶12</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p8\" data-pid=\"8\">Ang paglahutay sa mas lisod nga mga pagsulay sa umaabot gipakasama sa “pagpakiglumba sa mga kabayo” (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 12:5</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/2/0\"><em>w11</em> 3/15 32 ¶19</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p9\" data-pid=\"9\">Ang pag-ugmad sa atong gugma sa mga igsoon karon makatabang aron makalahutay ta panahon sa dakong kasakitan (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/3/0\" data-bid=\"4-1\" class=\"b\">Isa 26:20</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/3/0\"><em>w23.07</em> 6-7 ¶15-16</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f1\" class=\"south_center\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/234\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/233\" alt=\"Collage: 1. Grupo sa batan-ong mga Saksi nga malipayong nakigdula ug card uban sa edaran nga brader. 2. Ang mao ra gihapon nga mga Saksi nga naa nay ubang kauban, nagtuon sa Bibliya diha sa basement panahon sa dakong kasakitan.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" class=\"south_center\" />\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p10\" data-pid=\"10\"><strong>2. Espirituwal nga mga Bahandi</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt14\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt15\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p11\" data-pid=\"11\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"du-listStyleType--none du-padding-inlineStart--0\"><li><p id=\"p12\" data-pid=\"12\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/4/0\" data-bid=\"5-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 12:1,</a><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/4/1\" data-bid=\"5-2\" class=\"b\"> 3</a>—Unsay gipakita niini nga mga teksto bahin sa kasuod ni Jeremias kang Jehova? (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/4/0\"><em>jr</em> 118 ¶11</a>)</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p13\" data-pid=\"13\">\r\n<label for=\"tt20\" id=\"tt18\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt20\" name=\"textarea-1\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p14\" data-pid=\"14\">Unsang espirituwal nga mga bahandi ang imong nakat-onan sa pagbasa sa Bibliya niining semanaha?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p15\" data-pid=\"15\">\r\n<label for=\"tt25\" id=\"tt23\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt25\" name=\"textarea-2\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p16\" data-pid=\"16\"><strong>3. Pagbasa sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt28\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p17\" data-pid=\"17\">(4 min.) <a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/5/0\" data-bid=\"6-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 12:1-11</a> (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/5/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 2</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt29\" class=\"dc-icon--wheat dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--gold-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p18\" data-pid=\"18\"><strong>MAGMAEPEKTIBO SA MINISTERYO</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p19\" data-pid=\"19\"><strong>4. Dihang Magsugod ug Panag-estorya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt32\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p20\" data-pid=\"20\">(3 min.) IMPORMAL NGA PAGSANGYAW. Sugdi ang panag-estorya human nga ang usa ka tawo may gisulti o gihimo nga maayo. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/6/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 1 punto 4</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p21\" data-pid=\"21\"><strong>5. Dihang Makig-estorya Pag-usab</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt34\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p22\" data-pid=\"22\">(4 min.) PAGPAMALAYBALAY. Ginikanan ang imong kaestorya. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/7/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 3 punto 3</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p23\" data-pid=\"23\"><strong>6. Pakigpulong</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt36\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p24\" data-pid=\"24\">(5 min.) <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/8/0\"><em>lmd</em> apendise A punto 17</a>—Tema: Si Jesus Maayo Kaayo nga Magtutudlo ug ang Iyang mga Tambag Kanunayng Praktikal. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/9/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 14</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt37\" class=\"dc-icon--sheep dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--red-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p25\" data-pid=\"25\"><strong>KRISTOHANONG PAGKINABUHI</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base\" id=\"p26\" data-pid=\"26\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/10/0\"><strong>Awit 109</strong></a></h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p27\" data-pid=\"27\"><strong>7. Lokal nga mga Panginahanglan</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt42\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p28\" data-pid=\"28\">(15 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p29\" data-pid=\"29\"><strong>8. Pagtuon sa Kongregasyon sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt44\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p30\" data-pid=\"30\">(30 min.) <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/11/0\"><em>lfb</em> leksiyon 98-99</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-margin-top--12 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p31\" data-pid=\"31\"><strong>Konklusyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(3 min.)</span> <strong>|</strong> <span class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-inlineStart--2 dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026169/12/0\"><strong>Awit 69</strong></a></span> <strong>ug Pag-ampo</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n",
